    <text id="B0328T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Brower reports that Louisa Williams does not appear to be insane, and he would
                    like to discharge her if a home for her could be found.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Howards Grove Hospital
                    <name type="recipient">Thomas P. Jackson<lb/><abbr
                            expan="Assistant Sub Assistant Commissioner">Asst. Sub. Asst.
                        Comr.</abbr> Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands"
                            >R.F. and A.L.</abbr><lb/>4th <abbr expan="Division">Div.</abbr> 9th Sub
                            <abbr expan="District">Dist.</abbr> Virginia</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-03-29">March 29th 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Richmond, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir:</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to report that Louisa J. Williams, has not manifested any
                    symptoms of insanity for three (3) months.</p>

                <p>Her general health is very good. I would not hesitate to discharge her if she
                    could find a home among sympathizing friends.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am, Sir,<lb/>Very Respectfully,<lb/>Your <abbr expan="obedient"
                        >obt.</abbr> servant</salute>
                    <signed>D.R. Brower<lb/><abbr expan="Assistant Adjutant Surgeon">A. A. Surg.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="United States Army">USA</abbr><lb/>In charge of Hospital</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Thro': Office <abbr expan="Surgeon">Surg.</abbr> in <abbr
                            expan="Chief">chf.</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="District">Dist.</abbr> of
                            <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr><lb/>Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees">R.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Freedmen">F.</abbr> and <abbr expan="Abandoned">A.</abbr>
                    Lands</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
